[Feature] Student Edition of Artemis Eclipse (#168)

This PR introduces a student edition of Artemis Eclipse to work on programming tasks:
* Handling of exams and normal Java Programming tasks.
* Show test results as live feedback
* Handle multiple programming tasks in one workspace (only student edition)
* Show assessments of tutors that used the artemis grading plugin

Besides that it introduces ..

* A new layout of projects as the modules where spitted according to their purpose
* Increase compile time by building the actual eclipse products in their own profile
* Add a spotless formatter
